Title: Pokémon: Arceus and the Jewel of Life
Genre: Animation, Action, Adventure, Drama, Family, Fantasy, Sci-Fi
Writer: Hideki Sonoda (screenplay), Junichi Masuda (original concept), Ken Sugimori (original concept), Satoshi Tajiri (original concept)
Actors: Sarah Natochenny, Michele Knotz, Emily Bauer, James Carter Cathcart
Plot: Arceus, creator of the world, comes to pass judgement on humanity for the theft of the Jewel of Life, but Ash Ketchum and his friends are sent back in time to discover and possible reverse the events that led to Arceus' vendetta.
